Create a visual image generation prompt for a matrix cell.

Concept: "{concept}"
Context (use only as background framing, do not let it overshadow the concept): "{context}"

Generate a concise image generation prompt (1–2 sentences) that:
- Centres entirely on visually representing the concept — the context is secondary framing only
- Contains no text, words, or typography in the image
- Contains no real people, brands, logos, trademarked characters, or named intellectual property
- Is abstract, atmospheric, and evocative
- Works well as a card background image (square or portrait format)
- Uses color, texture, light, and composition to embody the concept
- Is visually distinct and striking

Output only the image generation prompt text — no JSON, no labels, no explanations. Just the prompt.
